CARIBBEAN SEA.
BONAIRE TO MARTINIQUE.
DNC 14.
1. 47 FOOT S/V PELENGINA 2, WHITE HULL WITH BLUE STRIPE,
   ONE PERSON ON BOARD, OVERDUE BONAIRE (12-11.0N 068-15.0W)
   TO MARTINIQUE (14-40.0N 061-00.0W). LAST KNOWN POSITION
   13-01.5N 069-51.9W AT 220339Z DEC 14. S/V POSSIBLY ADRIFT
   IN WESTERN CARIBBEAN SEA. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
   TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO JRCC CURACAO, PHONE: 599 9463 7700,
   E-MAIL: RCC.CURACAO@MINDEF.NL, RCC.CURACAO@GMAIL.COM.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 3173/14(24,25).
